        <h2>Intro to AI and ML</h2>
        <p>In a world accelerating at the speed of AI, understanding how these incredible capabilities get smarter is critical to driving business outcomes. Artificial intelligence (AI) is the theory of computer systems that can perform complex tasks. Machine learning (ML) is the process by which computers, including AI, learn new things; people use ML to feed data to the AI and train it over time.</p>

